OWNERS of empty homes in West Dunbartonshire can apply for loans so that they can carry out refurbishments before putting the property up for sale. Loans to aid house sales OWNERS of empty homes in West Dunbartonshire can apply for loans so that they can carry out refurbishments before putting the property up for sale.Council chiefs reckon the &quot;loan-to-sell&quot; scheme could bring empty properties back into use after the Government relaxed rules to make it easier to bring them up them to a habitable standard. 